{"tid":2415423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有圖慎入！綠鬣蜥遭殘殺「嘴塞鞭炮爆頭亡」網友轟：跟畜生沒兩樣","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T09:10:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eec7ce88310a047ff0e75bf493b773de6f49e9d2","tid":2415423,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7NjKgj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7NjKgj.png&h=a9d1482f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4yu6uH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4yu6uH.png&h=b8ed9f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外來種生物綠鬣蜥在台灣沒天敵，在台灣南部大量繁殖，啃食農作物和挖洞築巢，破壞台灣<br />\n農業生態。台灣也逐步展開移除作業，但有網友爆料，有惡劣人士仗著移除外來種的名義，<br />\n慘忍殺害綠鬣蜥為樂，甚至把鞭炮放進嘴裡，讓牠活活被炸死，網友也怒轟「這樣跟畜生沒<br />\n什麼兩樣」。<br />\n <br />\n網友在臉書「爆怨公社」指出，自己熱愛綠鬣蜥，也是一名飼主，近來有一堆人仗著移除外<br />\n來種的名號，以虐殺綠鬣蜥為樂趣，甚至有人把鞭炮塞進牠們嘴裡，讓牠們活活被炸死，慘<br />\n死的屍體還到處亂丟，讓原po氣炸「同樣是外來種，待遇怎麼差這麼多，只是差在沒有法律<br />\n保護就可以不尊重生命嗎？連一點道德都沒有，還在沾沾自喜幫農夫移除外來種」她也說「<br />\n我支持移除外來種，但同時是否能請各位『正義』的大俠尊重一下生命？不然你們跟畜生沒<br />\n什麼兩樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.tw/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/7320/5262934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.tw%2Famp%2Fs%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F7320%2F5262934&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=5d7ed373\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.tw/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/7320/5262934</a>"},{"pid":"8c247805bf54574c12f5ceb985a77117499f45e5","tid":2415423,"uid":199162,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97470d34ff78fd3554806bcc7a8cd418fa342ace","tid":2415423,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:45:56.000Z","msg":"有冇原圖"},{"pid":"f6e5687a1ff8a34b10d093cf130f3bb934796387","tid":2415423,"uid":204429,"like":2,"dislike"